{"tid":672133,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"［冷門］L39 LTM 鏡頭討論帖","createTime":"2018-05-20T17:06:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T15:08:34.000Z","uid":12449,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"589ed1d1564ddf0e05bd8293490f376868875f9b","tid":672133,"uid":12449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T17:06:11.000Z","msg":"呢個post主要係集中搜集LTM，希望可以整合埋中文資料零散嘅Leica螺絲接口鏡頭資訊，大家有咩意見都可以拎出嚟講，有錯嘅話任屌唔嬲，不妨指正。<br />\n<br />\n介紹：M39 M42就聽得多，L39又咩嚟？<br />\nL解Leica，39指螺絲口。<br />\nL39同M39嘅不同之處，在於一般嘅M39唔支持Leica screw mount嘅連動測距對焦。用Leica Thread Mount (LTM)嘅用家絕對要留意，唔係買咗返嚟唔岩用又要賣返出去。<br />\n<br />\n作為leica嘅早期鏡頭，想將呢類老鏡安裝係M系，只要加L39-M adapter轉換就可以同平時一樣正確對焦。而無反相機都一樣裝轉換就用到。<br />\n<br />\n其實除咗Leica出產嘅機身之外，Canon Nikon等公司，特別係蘇聯，甚至係英國公司，都出產過對應LTM嘅機身。<br />\n歷史因素：因為當時德國戰敗，同盟國公開有關Leica嘅鏡頭同機身專利及設計圖。呢個亦係主要原因令市面上會存在大量外形同Leica相似嘅款，當中有啲機身係進一步發展成為今日我哋熟悉嘅相機品牌，有啲就發展停滯消失咗蹤影。買之前搵下資料先，唔好貪平，因為呢啲機郁啲都有60年以上嘅歷史，仲用唔用得耐都係要注意。遲啲可能會講吓螺絲接口嘅機身<br />\n<br />\nLeica 原廠鏡頭分類名稱：<br />\n<br />\nf/0.95, f/1 and f/1.2\tNOCTILUX<br />\nf/1.4\tSUMMILUX<br />\nf/2\tSUMMICRON<br />\nf/2.5\tSUMMARIT<br />\nf/2.8\tELMARIT<br />\nf/3.5, f/3.8 and f/4\tELMAR, SUPER-ELMAR<br />\nf/4.5\tHEKTOR<br />\n<br />\n暫時搵到嘅資料係光圈數值愈細，個價錢仲愈貴，應該係同生產量有關。原廠最貴見過5萬蚊，平嘅1千都有都有，豐儉由人。俄仔鏡就仲平啲，反而Canon 同 Nikkor仲介乎1千至4千蚊。"},{"pid":"ebe015d9cfc1eef84982dd71acb39c3d49b6abb9","tid":672133,"uid":12449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T17:10:49.000Z","msg":"介紹第一支鏡頭 <br />\nLEICA ELMAR 50mm f/3.5 (二手價大約係HK$2000)<br />\n<br />\n最大特色係可以縮入機身嘅鏡頭，而且鏡頭體積好鬼細粒，唔知有冇平時鏡頭嘅一半，未度過。<br />\n<br />\n實測彩色照片：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/010733_e97b17c32764b77463c901f1f1e59f08.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F010733_e97b17c32764b77463c901f1f1e59f08.png&h=69fa9334&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/010743_9b81ad3a73fea297e31a8fa703e02e35.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F010743_9b81ad3a73fea297e31a8fa703e02e35.png&h=c9be3414&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日間同夜晚嘅效果，可以見到顏色嘅層次感都好強，但由於我冇M系嘅鏡頭做比較，所以就唔知奶味夠唔夠"},{"pid":"414d97d3459b6f3b63840ae6f178626227b89424","tid":672133,"uid":12449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T17:12:40.000Z","msg":"LEICA ELMAR 50mm f/3.5<br />\n補返張圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/011238_374172b20d43a9f7464ee9a8bd55fa75.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F011238_374172b20d43a9f7464ee9a8bd55fa75.png&h=efa3f3ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8df1d635d4d51aa69ba61472150f51854aabf2fa","tid":672133,"uid":174601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T17:13:17.000Z","msg":"留明學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cec6fbae66fd75fce7cdafa522651ee14edfcf80","tid":672133,"uid":43493,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T17:19:58.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"672d3515ebfb1c7d451152858c438ab6e486e1c0","tid":672133,"uid":25516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T17:51:26.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"f1d3d27d0275911bfc9594eedb27f721fb0abdc8","tid":672133,"uid":31973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T00:03:09.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"87c07822471a762f65b97e51f0f601ce80605304","tid":672133,"uid":12592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T02:37:19.000Z","msg":"想請教下如果係裝上A7配神力環玩,LTM-M環洗唔洗照翻28/35/50焦段咁買?定可以一個環玩哂? Thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41041848e2b275a41d7eefca9f1cbb8e6e22245c","tid":672133,"uid":14625,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T02:55:55.000Z","msg":"冇summitar<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f3123ccdd1b89fa72bf39274925148a7fd4825","tid":672133,"uid":31973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87c07822471a762f65b97e51f0f601ce80605304","tid":672133,"uid":12592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T02:37:19.000Z","msg":"想請教下如果係裝上A7配神力環玩,LTM-M環洗唔洗照翻28/35/50焦段咁買?定可以一個環玩哂? Thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T02:59:54.000Z","msg":"唔使, 不過配返一樣會好啲, 將來玩leica 機/放鏡都方便啲嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea23ae45caa95ffa52e0962e961ddc320e12ad49","tid":672133,"uid":12449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87c07822471a762f65b97e51f0f601ce80605304","tid":672133,"uid":12592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T02:37:19.000Z","msg":"想請教下如果係裝上A7配神力環玩,LTM-M環洗唔洗照翻28/35/50焦段咁買?定可以一個環玩哂? Thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T03:12:51.000Z","msg":"不同焦段嘅LTM鏡頭都可以用同一個轉接環駁去Sony A7 到用。<br />\n<br />\n題外話：轉接環嘅功用係增加Flange Focal distance (法蘭距) 則係鏡頭接環至菲林或感光元件。Sony E 係18.0mm 而 Leica M係27.8mm 另外 LTM 係28.8mm。所以 LTM可以放去Sony E 同Leica M 到用。<br />\n<br />\n但 LTM 除咗接口口徑細裝唔上，連法蘭距都長過人哋。當焦距比較長嘅時候，接上短焦距鏡時，就會出現無限焦距失效嘅情況，好似近視咁。因此有啲接環會加塊鏡片修正呢個問題。<br />\n<br />\n相信你之後都會試其他廠嘅鏡頭，可以參考呢個表去買接環<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/110756_e886e59f1ac68ba481ba864adb84bfc0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F110756_e886e59f1ac68ba481ba864adb84bfc0.jpg&h=53379dc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於Sony E係無反，法蘭距係屬於短距，基本上除咗 Pentax Q, Nikon 1, Fujifilm X 同Canon EF-M 之外，其他鏡頭法蘭距都短過Sony E，可以正常，不過有啲自動化功能會用唔到，例如自動對焦同光圈優先 (A mode)。"},{"pid":"ddb3af05d8d5570622ababfb33d059a4fe9c765f","tid":672133,"uid":12449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41041848e2b275a41d7eefca9f1cbb8e6e22245c","tid":672133,"uid":14625,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T02:55:55.000Z","msg":"冇summitar<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T03:15:42.000Z","msg":"我晏啲會逐支鏡頭講吓，因為LTM雖然年紀老，但持續開發時段都有30年左右，原廠都有成30支左右。"},{"pid":"521db66fa2c239b95b5baf432e4208e0aaf82072","tid":672133,"uid":79632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T03:37:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但 LTM 除咗接口口徑細裝唔上，連法蘭距都長過人哋。當焦距比較長嘅時候，接上短焦距鏡時，就會出現無限焦距失效嘅情況，好似近視咁。因此有啲接環會加塊鏡片修正呢個問題。<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n關焦距事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a33292e7611486d707c11aeee833521a4610c944","tid":672133,"uid":12449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"521db66fa2c239b95b5baf432e4208e0aaf82072","tid":672133,"uid":79632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T03:37:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但 LTM 除咗接口口徑細裝唔上，連法蘭距都長過人哋。當焦距比較長嘅時候，接上短焦距鏡時，就會出現無限焦距失效嘅情況，好似近視咁。因此有啲接環會加塊鏡片修正呢個問題。<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n關焦距事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T03:38:20.000Z","msg":"應該係法蘭距 筆誤"},{"pid":"aa4af1c27bbf1cd8762bd17b92dbc86f9367deab","tid":672133,"uid":78755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T04:45:03.000Z","msg":"支持，留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cee5df2824ae3fcc08778c2c26583421c999eee","tid":672133,"uid":33310,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T17:10:33.000Z","msg":"Leitz Summar 5cm F2<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/22/010914_22bdcb4a69ae66fd38cf635f9e58c25f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F22%2F010914_22bdcb4a69ae66fd38cf635f9e58c25f.png&h=81aff981&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/22/010930_dac3a649be1f10ed110db04c977b506a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"http